---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Live Coaching - PBL Future Labs">
    <!-- Page Header -->
    <section class="scroll-reveal px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8" style="padding: 4rem 0 3rem;">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <h1 class="mb-4">Live Coaching.</h1>
            <p style="color: #a0a0a0; font-size: 1.1rem; max-width: 520px;">Work directly with Thom Markham, Ph.D. and Phil Alcock. Personalized guidance for educators and school teams implementing AI + PBL.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="section-divider"></div>

    <!-- Coaching Tiers -->
    <section class="scroll-reveal px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8" style="padding: 2rem 0 3rem;">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="mb-4">Choose your format.</h2>
            <p class="mb-10" style="color: #a0a0a0; max-width: 480px;">Whether you need a quick strategy call or ongoing partnership, we have the right option for you.</p>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                <!-- Tier 1: Quick Consult -->
                <div class="coaching-tier-card">
                    <p style="color: #E33D5A; font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.8rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Getting started</p>
                    <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Quick Consult</h3>
                    <p style="color: #a0a0a0; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">A focused 30-minute conversation to answer your most pressing PBL + AI questions.</p>
                    <p style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 500; color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Free</p>
                    <p style="color: #a0a0a0; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">30 minutes, virtual</p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6" style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #a0a0a0;">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: #E33D5A;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                            Needs assessment
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: #E33D5A;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                            Quick-win recommendations
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: #E33D5A;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                            No obligation
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <a href="mailto:hello@pblfuturelabs.com?subject=Quick Consult Request" class="btn-primary-teal w-full text-center" style="display: block;">Book a call</a>
                </div>

                <!-- Tier 2: Deep Dive -->
                <div class="coaching-tier-card coaching-tier-featured">
                    <p style="color: #E33D5A; font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.8rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Most popular</p>
                    <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Deep Dive</h3>
                    <p style="color: #a0a0a0; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">A 60-minute focused session to solve a specific challenge or design a PBL implementation plan.</p>
                    <p style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 500; color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">$249</p>
                    <p style="color: #a0a0a0; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">60 minutes, virtual or in-person</p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6" style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #a0a0a0;">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: #E33D5A;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                            Focused problem-solving
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: #E33D5A;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                            Custom action plan
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: #E33D5A;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                            Follow-up email summary
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: #E33D5A;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                            Resource recommendations
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <a href="mailto:hello@pblfuturelabs.com?subject=Deep Dive Coaching Request" class="btn-primary-teal w-full text-center" style="display: block;">Book a session</a>
                </div>

                <!-- Tier 3: Ongoing Partnership -->
                <div class="coaching-tier-card">
                    <p style="color: #E33D5A; font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.8rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">For schools & districts</p>
                    <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Ongoing Partnership</h3>
                    <p style="color: #a0a0a0; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Monthly retainer for schools and districts. Sustained coaching, workshops, and implementation support.</p>
                    <p style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 500; color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Custom</p>
                    <p style="color: #a0a0a0; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Monthly, virtual + in-person</p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6" style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #a0a0a0;">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: #E33D5A;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                            School-wide PBL rollout
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: #E33D5A;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                            Teacher workshops
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: #E33D5A;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                            Leadership coaching
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: #E33D5A;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                            Custom curriculum design
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <a href="mailto:hello@pblfuturelabs.com?subject=Partnership Inquiry" class="btn-primary-teal w-full text-center" style="display: block;">Get in touch</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="section-divider"></div>

    <!-- Session Types -->
    <section class="scroll-reveal px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8" style="padding: 2rem 0 3rem;">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="mb-10">Session types.</h2>
            <div class="space-y-10">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="mb-2">1:1 Coaching</h3>
                    <p style="color: #a0a0a0;">Personalized sessions for individual educators looking to implement AI + PBL in their classroom. Walk away with a concrete plan and specific tools.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="divider-line"></div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="mb-2">Small Group</h3>
                    <p style="color: #a0a0a0;">Ideal for department teams or grade-level groups (3-8 educators). Collaborative planning with hands-on practice designing AI-enhanced projects together.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="divider-line"></div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="mb-2">School Team</h3>
                    <p style="color: #a0a0a0;">Full staff workshops and multi-session implementation support. Includes leadership coaching, teacher training, and curriculum design assistance.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="section-divider"></div>

    <!-- What You Walk Away With -->
    <section class="scroll-reveal px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8" style="padding: 2rem 0 3rem;">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="mb-10">What you walk away with.</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="mb-2" style="font-size: 1rem;">A clear implementation plan</h3>
                    <p style="color: #a0a0a0; font-size: 0.9rem;">Step-by-step roadmap tailored to your school's context, standards, and student needs.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="mb-2" style="font-size: 1rem;">Ready-to-use AI prompts</h3>
                    <p style="color: #a0a0a0; font-size: 0.9rem;">Tested prompts and workflows for project design, differentiation, and assessment.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="mb-2" style="font-size: 1rem;">PBL frameworks</h3>
                    <p style="color: #a0a0a0; font-size: 0.9rem;">Proven project design templates from Thom Markham's methodology — grounded in 15+ years of research.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="mb-2" style="font-size: 1rem;">Ongoing confidence</h3>
                    <p style="color: #a0a0a0; font-size: 0.9rem;">The knowledge and support to keep implementing long after the session ends.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="section-divider"></div>

    <!-- Your Coaches -->
    <section class="scroll-reveal px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8" style="padding: 2rem 0 3rem;">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="mb-10">Your coaches.</h2>
            <div class="space-y-12">
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 items-start">
                    <div class="w-32 h-32 flex-shrink-0 overflow-hidden img-skeleton" style="border-radius: 8px;">
                        <img src="/images/thom.webp" alt="Thom Markham, Ph.D." width="128" height="128" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" decoding="async" onload="this.parentElement.classList.add('loaded')" />
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="mb-1">Thom Markham, Ph.D.</h3>
                        <p class="mb-3" style="color: #E33D5A; font-size: 0.85rem;">Author & PBL Expert</p>
                        <p style="color: #a0a0a0;">Author of three bestselling PBL books, including <em style="color: #ffffff;">Project-Based Learning Handbook</em>. Ph.D. in Psychology. Thom has trained thousands of educators across 15+ years and brings deep expertise in learning science, project design, and assessment to every coaching session.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="divider-line"></div>
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 items-start">
                    <div class="w-32 h-32 flex-shrink-0" style="border-radius: 8px; background-color: #1a1a1a; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">
                        <span style="font-size: 2.5rem; color: #a0a0a0;">PA</span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="mb-1">Phil Alcock</h3>
                        <p class="mb-3" style="color: #E33D5A; font-size: 0.85rem;">Founder, PBL Future Labs</p>
                        <p style="color: #a0a0a0;">Australian educator based in Acapulco, Mexico. Phil has spoken at ISTE, guest lectured at Harvard, and built a following of 10,000+ educators on LinkedIn. He specializes in AI integration frameworks and practical classroom applications.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="section-divider"></div>

    <!-- Testimonials -->
    <section class="scroll-reveal px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8" style="padding: 2rem 0 3rem;">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="mb-10">What educators say.</h2>
            <div class="space-y-8">
                <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl" style="background-color: #1a1a1a; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);">
                    <p style="color: #d1d5db; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 1rem;">"The coaching session with Thom and Phil gave our team a completely new perspective on how to use AI in our PBL units. We left with a concrete plan and tools we could use the next day."</p>
                    <p style="color: #ffffff; font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.9rem;">— Department Chair, International School, Singapore</p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl" style="background-color: #1a1a1a; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);">
                    <p style="color: #d1d5db; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 1rem;">"Phil's deep dive session helped me redesign my entire unit using AI tools I didn't even know existed. My students are producing work at a level I've never seen before."</p>
                    <p style="color: #ffffff; font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.9rem;">— High school science teacher, Texas</p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl" style="background-color: #1a1a1a; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);">
                    <p style="color: #d1d5db; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 1rem;">"The ongoing partnership has been transformative for our school. Thom's expertise in PBL combined with the AI frameworks has given our teachers confidence to innovate."</p>
                    <p style="color: #ffffff; font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.9rem;">— Principal, Charter School Network, California</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="section-divider"></div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="scroll-reveal text-center px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8" style="padding: 2rem 0 4rem;">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="mb-4">Ready to start?</h2>
            <p class="mb-8" style="color: #a0a0a0; max-width: 420px; margin: 0 auto;">Your first conversation is free. Tell us about your school and we'll recommend the best path forward.</p>
            <a href="mailto:hello@pblfuturelabs.com?subject=Coaching Inquiry" class="btn-primary-teal">Book a free call &rarr;</a>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
